transaksyon gamit ang BTC para sa mga Tracfone refill card.\"},{\"locale\":\"vi\",\"reviewBody\":\"Giao dịch hoàn hảo sử dụng BTC cho thẻ nạp Tracfone.\"},{\"locale\":\"zh\",\"reviewBody\":\"使用BTC购买Tracfone充值卡的交易非常完美。\"},{\"locale\":\"pt\",\"reviewBody\":\"Transação perfeita usando BTC para cartões de recarga Tracfone.\"},{\"locale\":\"hi\",\"reviewBody\":\"Tracfone रिफिल कार्ड के लिए BTC का उपयोग करके परफेक्ट ट्रांजैक्शन।\"},{\"locale\":\"pl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Idealna transakcja z użyciem BTC na karty doładowujące Tracfone.\"},{\"locale\":\"id\",\"reviewBody\":\"Transaksi sempurna menggunakan BTC untuk kartu isi ulang Tracfone.\"},{\"locale\":\"ja\",\"reviewBody\":\"TracfoneのリフィルカードにBTCを使った完璧な取引。\"},{\"locale\":\"ko\",\"reviewBody\":\"Tracfone 충전 카드에 BTC를 사용한 완벽한 거래.\"}],\"_fingerprint\":\"f7307f1deeee11f236c258bbe3cf9bc5dbab376191c0a41e3770a26b76b90533\"},{\"name\":\"Dmitry Sad\",\"reviewBody\":\"Fantastic service for any country phone top-up.\",\"language\":\"en\",\"reviewRating\":5,\"datePublished\":\"2026-06-14\",\"platform\":\"cryptorefills\",\"url\":null,\"image\":null,\"kinds\":[\"mobile_recharges\"],\"isoCodes\":[\"BR\"],\"brands\":[\"Vodafone Credits\"],\"translations\":[{\"locale\":\"de\",\"reviewBody\":\"Fantastischer Service für Aufladungen von Handys in jedem Land.\"},{\"locale\":\"es\",\"reviewBody\":\"Servicio fantástico para recargas de teléfono en cualquier país.\"},{\"locale\":\"it\",\"reviewBody\":\"Servizio fantastico per ricariche telefoniche in qualsiasi paese.\"},{\"locale\":\"tr\",\"reviewBody\":\"Her ülke telefonu kontör yüklemesi için harika hizmet.\"},{\"locale\":\"fr\",\"reviewBody\":\"Service fantastique pour la recharge de téléphone dans n'importe quel pays.\"},{\"locale\":\"tl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Kamangha-manghang serbisyo para sa top-up ng telepono sa anumang bansa.\"},{\"locale\":\"vi\",\"reviewBody\":\"Dịch vụ tuyệt vời cho việc nạp tiền điện thoại ở bất kỳ quốc gia nào.\"},{\"locale\":\"zh\",\"reviewBody\":\"为任何国家的手机充值提供了极好的服务。\"},{\"locale\":\"pt\",\"reviewBody\":\"Serviço fantástico para recarga de telefone em qualquer país.\"},{\"locale\":\"hi\",\"reviewBody\":\"किसी भी देश के फोन टॉप-अप के लिए शानदार सेवा।\"},{\"locale\":\"pl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Fantastyczna obsługa do doładowań telefonów w każdym kraju.\"},{\"locale\":\"id\",\"reviewBody\":\"Layanan fantastis untuk isi ulang telepon di negara mana pun.\"},{\"locale\":\"ja\",\"reviewBody\":\"どの国の携帯電話のチャージにも素晴らしいサービスです。\"},{\"locale\":\"ko\",\"reviewBody\":\"어느 나라 휴대폰 충전에도 환상적인 서비스입니다.\"}],\"_fingerprint\":\"431f1baf11240d5006a9b275d88d5357063fed9fd31df6b019fbb6436bb0cfca\"},{\"name\":\"AJ\",\"reviewBody\":\"Works great and is fast\",\"language\":\"en\",\"reviewRating\":5,\"datePublished\":\"2026-06-13\",\"platform\":\"cryptorefills\",\"url\":null,\"image\":null,\"kinds\":[\"giftcards\"],\"isoCodes\":[\"DE\"],\"brands\":[\"Steam\"],\"translations\":[{\"locale\":\"de\",\"reviewBody\":\"Funktioniert großartig und ist schnell\"},{\"locale\":\"es\",\"reviewBody\":\"Funciona muy bien y es rápido\"},{\"locale\":\"it\",\"reviewBody\":\"Funziona alla grande ed è veloce\"},{\"locale\":\"tr\",\"reviewBody\":\"Harika çalışıyor ve hızlı\"},{\"locale\":\"fr\",\"reviewBody\":\"Fonctionne très bien et est rapide\"},{\"locale\":\"tl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Mabisa at mabilis\"},{\"locale\":\"vi\",\"reviewBody\":\"Hoạt động tốt và nhanh\"},{\"locale\":\"zh\",\"reviewBody\":\"效果很好且速度快\"},{\"locale\":\"pt\",\"reviewBody\":\"Funciona muito bem e é rápido\"},{\"locale\":\"hi\",\"reviewBody\":\"बहुत अच्छा काम करता है और तेज है\"},{\"locale\":\"pl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Działa świetnie i jest szybki\"},{\"locale\":\"id\",\"reviewBody\":\"Bekerja dengan baik dan cepat\"},{\"locale\":\"ja\",\"reviewBody\":\"よく動作し、速いです\"},{\"locale\":\"ko\",\"reviewBody\":\"잘 작동하고 빠릅니다\"}],\"_fingerprint\":\"4d858f7e0e3316716ef678d9a0c244b3eebaa2e2a808403fe2e74ccd2f79c50c\"},{\"name\":\"Thomas\",\"reviewBody\":\"Worked exactly as advertised. As soon as payment cleared (5min) the PIN \u0026 Serial were immediately delivered via email. Will definitely use again.\",\"language\":\"en\",\"reviewRating\":5,\"datePublished\":\"2026-06-13\",\"platform\":\"cryptorefills\",\"url\":null,\"image\":null,\"kinds\":[\"mobile_recharges\"],\"isoCodes\":[\"US\"],\"brands\":[\"Tracfone USA Credits\"],\"translations\":[{\"locale\":\"de\",\"reviewBody\":\"Funktionierte genau wie beworben. Sobald die Zahlung bestätigt war (5 Min), wurden PIN und Seriennummer sofort per E-Mail geliefert. Werde definitiv wieder hier kaufen.\"},{\"locale\":\"es\",\"reviewBody\":\"Funcionó exactamente como se anunciaba. Tan pronto como se confirmó el pago (5 minutos), el PIN y el número de serie se enviaron inmediatamente por correo electrónico. Definitivamente volveré a usarlo.\"},{\"locale\":\"it\",\"reviewBody\":\"Ha funzionato esattamente come pubblicizzato. Non appena il pagamento è stato confermato (5 minuti), il PIN e il numero di serie sono stati immediatamente inviati via email. Sicuramente lo userò di nuovo.\"},{\"locale\":\"tr\",\"reviewBody\":\"Reklam edildiği gibi çalıştı. Ödeme onaylanır onaylanmaz (5 dakika) PIN ve Seri Numarası hemen e-posta ile teslim edildi. Kesinlikle tekrar kullanacağım.\"},{\"locale\":\"fr\",\"reviewBody\":\"Fonctionne exactement comme annoncé. Dès que le paiement a été validé (5 minutes), le code PIN et le numéro de série ont été immédiatement envoyés par e-mail. Je l'utiliserai certainement à nouveau.\"},{\"locale\":\"tl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Gumana nang eksakto ayon sa ipinangako. Pagkatapos ma-clear ang bayad (5 minuto), agad na naipadala ang PIN at Serial sa pamamagitan ng email. Tiyak na gagamitin ko ulit.\"},{\"locale\":\"vi\",\"reviewBody\":\"Hoạt động chính xác như quảng cáo. Ngay khi thanh toán được xác nhận (5 phút), mã PIN và số serial đã được gửi ngay qua email. Chắc chắn sẽ sử dụng lại.\"},{\"locale\":\"zh\",\"reviewBody\":\"完全按照广告所说的那样工作。付款一确认（5分钟内），PIN码和序列号立即通过电子邮件发送。肯定会再次使用。\"},{\"locale\":\"pt\",\"reviewBody\":\"Funcionou exatamente como anunciado. Assim que o pagamento foi confirmado (5 minutos), o PIN e o número de série foram imediatamente enviados por e-mail. Com certeza usarei novamente.\"},{\"locale\":\"hi\",\"reviewBody\":\"विज्ञापन के अनुसार बिल्कुल काम किया। भुगतान क्लियर होते ही (5 मिनट में) PIN और सीरियल तुरंत ईमेल के माध्यम से भेज दिए गए। निश्चित रूप से फिर से उपयोग करूंगा।\"},{\"locale\":\"pl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Działało dokładnie tak, jak reklamowano. Gdy tylko płatność została zaksięgowana (5 minut), PIN i numer seryjny zostały natychmiast dostarczone e-mailem. Zdecydowanie skorzystam ponownie.\"},{\"locale\":\"id\",\"reviewBody\":\"Bekerja persis seperti yang diiklankan. Begitu pembayaran dikonfirmasi (5 menit), PIN \u0026 Serial langsung dikirim melalui email. Pasti akan menggunakan lagi.\"},{\"locale\":\"ja\",\"reviewBody\":\"広告通りに正確に動作しました。支払いが確認されるとすぐに（5分以内）、PINとシリアルがすぐにメールで届きました。間違いなくまた利用します。\"},{\"locale\":\"ko\",\"reviewBody\":\"광고한 대로 정확히 작동했습니다. 결제가 완료되자마자(5분 내) PIN과 시리얼이 즉시 이메일로 전달되었습니다. 꼭 다시 이용할 것입니다.\"}],\"_fingerprint\":\"25d3da5dbad08adb1f4dbe228d9b065a68087bf2e4d5b97ee54963abfbed5680\"},{\"name\":\"karlapudi naresh\",\"reviewBody\":\"I recently ordered a Big Basket gift vouchers on Cryptorefills the process was super simple. \\n\\nI just had to choose a crypto which was fast and voucher was delivered to me in a minute ❤️🖤\",\"language\":\"en\",\"reviewRating\":5,\"datePublished\":\"2026-06-10\",\"platform\":\"trustpilot\",\"url\":\"https://www.trustpilot.com/reviews/6a28e97407fa0550c7bbebb0\",\"image\":null,\"kinds\":[],\"isoCodes\":[],\"brands\":[],\"translations\":[{\"locale\":\"de\",\"reviewBody\":\"Ich habe kürzlich Big Basket-Geschenkgutscheine bei Cryptorefills bestellt, der Prozess war super einfach.\\n\\nIch musste nur eine Kryptowährung auswählen, was schnell ging, und der Gutschein wurde mir innerhalb einer Minute geliefert ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"es\",\"reviewBody\":\"Recientemente pedí vales de regalo de Big Basket en Cryptorefills, el proceso fue súper sencillo.\\n\\nSolo tuve que elegir una criptomoneda, que fue rápido, y el vale me fue entregado en un minuto ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"it\",\"reviewBody\":\"Ho ordinato di recente dei buoni regalo Big Basket su Cryptorefills, il processo è stato super semplice.\\n\\nHo dovuto solo scegliere una criptovaluta, che è stata veloce, e il voucher mi è stato consegnato in un minuto ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"tr\",\"reviewBody\":\"Yakın zamanda Cryptorefills üzerinden Big Basket hediye çekleri sipariş ettim, süreç çok basitti.\\n\\nSadece hızlı olan bir kripto para seçmem gerekiyordu ve çek bana bir dakika içinde teslim edildi ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"fr\",\"reviewBody\":\"J'ai récemment commandé des bons cadeaux Big Basket sur Cryptorefills, le processus a été super simple.\\n\\nJ'ai juste eu à choisir une crypto, ce qui a été rapide, et le bon m'a été livré en une minute ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"tl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Kamakailan lang ay umorder ako ng Big Basket gift vouchers sa Cryptorefills, napakadali ng proseso.\\n\\nKailangan ko lang pumili ng crypto na mabilis, at naipadala sa akin ang voucher sa loob ng isang minuto ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"vi\",\"reviewBody\":\"Gần đây tôi đã đặt mua phiếu quà tặng Big Basket trên Cryptorefills, quá trình rất đơn giản.\\n\\nTôi chỉ cần chọn một loại tiền điện tử nhanh và phiếu quà tặng đã được gửi đến tôi trong vòng một phút ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"zh\",\"reviewBody\":\"我最近在Cryptorefills订购了Big Basket礼品券，过程非常简单。\\n\\n我只需选择一种快速的加密货币，礼品券一分钟内就送达了我手中 ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"pt\",\"reviewBody\":\"Recentemente, pedi vouchers de presente Big Basket na Cryptorefills, o processo foi super simples.\\n\\nSó precisei escolher uma criptomoeda rápida e o voucher foi entregue a mim em um minuto ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"hi\",\"reviewBody\":\"मैंने हाल ही में Cryptorefills पर Big Basket गिफ्ट वाउचर ऑर्डर किए, प्रक्रिया बहुत सरल थी।\\n\\nमुझे बस एक तेज़ क्रिप्टो चुनना था और वाउचर मुझे एक मिनट में मिल गया ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"pl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Niedawno zamówiłem vouchery upominkowe Big Basket na Cryptorefills, proces był bardzo prosty.\\n\\nMusiałem tylko wybrać szybką kryptowalutę, a voucher został dostarczony do mnie w minutę ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"id\",\"reviewBody\":\"Saya baru saja memesan voucher hadiah Big Basket di Cryptorefills, prosesnya sangat mudah.\\n\\nSaya hanya perlu memilih crypto yang cepat dan voucher dikirimkan kepada saya dalam satu menit ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"ja\",\"reviewBody\":\"最近、CryptorefillsでBig Basketのギフト券を注文しましたが、手続きはとても簡単でした。\\n\\n速い暗号通貨を選ぶだけで、ギフト券は1分で届きました ❤️🖤\"},{\"locale\":\"ko\",\"reviewBody\":\"최근에 Cryptorefills에서 Big Basket 기프트 바우처를 주문했는데, 과정이 매우 간단했습니다.\\n\\n빠른 암호화폐를 선택하기만 하면 바우처가 1분 만에 전달되었습니다 ❤️🖤\"}],\"_fingerprint\":\"fc11f809b2ef929729e63cb1e9dd6b4c41acb8dee4ccf44fe7534b594e272a1a\"},{\"name\":\"Pavan Kumar\",\"reviewBody\":\"I bought a Vijay Sales Offline gift card today on crypto refills.\\n\\nThe process of buying and payment is very hassle free.\\n\\nI'll definitely choose crypto refills next time.\",\"language\":\"en\",\"reviewRating\":5,\"datePublished\":\"2026-06-10\",\"platform\":\"trustpilot\",\"url\":\"https://www.trustpilot.com/reviews/6a29654e545222d78dd5855c\",\"image\":null,\"kinds\":[],\"isoCodes\":[],\"brands\":[],\"translations\":[{\"locale\":\"de\",\"reviewBody\":\"Ich habe heute eine Vijay Sales Offline-Geschenkkarte bei Crypto Refills gekauft.\\n\\nDer Kauf- und Bezahlvorgang ist sehr unkompliziert.\\n\\nIch werde beim nächsten Mal definitiv Crypto Refills wählen.\"},{\"locale\":\"es\",\"reviewBody\":\"Hoy compré una tarjeta de regalo offline de Vijay Sales en Crypto Refills.\\n\\nEl proceso de compra y pago es muy sencillo.\\n\\nDefinitivamente elegiré Crypto Refills la próxima vez.\"},{\"locale\":\"it\",\"reviewBody\":\"Oggi ho acquistato una gift card offline Vijay Sales su Crypto Refills.\\n\\nIl processo di acquisto e pagamento è molto semplice.\\n\\nLa prossima volta sceglierò sicuramente Crypto Refills.\"},{\"locale\":\"tr\",\"reviewBody\":\"Bugün Crypto Refills üzerinden Vijay Sales Offline hediye kartı aldım.\\n\\nSatın alma ve ödeme süreci çok sorunsuz.\\n\\nBir dahaki sefere kesinlikle Crypto Refills'i tercih edeceğim.\"},{\"locale\":\"fr\",\"reviewBody\":\"J'ai acheté aujourd'hui une carte cadeau Vijay Sales hors ligne sur Crypto Refills.\\n\\nLe processus d'achat et de paiement est très simple.\\n\\nJe choisirai certainement Crypto Refills la prochaine fois.\"},{\"locale\":\"tl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Bumili ako ng Vijay Sales Offline gift card ngayon sa Crypto Refills.\\n\\nNapakadali ng proseso ng pagbili at pagbabayad.\\n\\nTiyak na pipiliin ko ang Crypto Refills sa susunod.\"},{\"locale\":\"vi\",\"reviewBody\":\"Hôm nay tôi đã mua thẻ quà tặng Vijay Sales Offline trên Crypto Refills.\\n\\nQuá trình mua và thanh toán rất thuận tiện.\\n\\nLần tới tôi chắc chắn sẽ chọn Crypto Refills.\"},{\"locale\":\"zh\",\"reviewBody\":\"我今天在Crypto Refills购买了一张Vijay Sales线下礼品卡。\\n\\n购买和支付过程非常便捷。\\n\\n下次我一定会选择Crypto Refills。\"},{\"locale\":\"pt\",\"reviewBody\":\"Comprei hoje um cartão presente offline da Vijay Sales na Crypto Refills.\\n\\nO processo de compra e pagamento é muito simples.\\n\\nDefinitivamente escolherei a Crypto Refills na próxima vez.\"},{\"locale\":\"hi\",\"reviewBody\":\"मैंने आज Crypto Refills पर Vijay Sales ऑफलाइन गिफ्ट कार्ड खरीदा।\\n\\nखरीदने और भुगतान करने की प्रक्रिया बहुत आसान है।\\n\\nअगली बार मैं निश्चित रूप से Crypto Refills चुनूंगा।\"},{\"locale\":\"pl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Dziś kupiłem kartę podarunkową Vijay Sales Offline na Crypto Refills.\\n\\nProces zakupu i płatności jest bardzo prosty.\\n\\nNa pewno wybiorę Crypto Refills następnym razem.\"},{\"locale\":\"id\",\"reviewBody\":\"Saya membeli kartu hadiah Vijay Sales Offline hari ini di Crypto Refills.\\n\\nProses pembelian dan pembayaran sangat mudah.\\n\\nSaya pasti akan memilih Crypto Refills lain kali.\"},{\"locale\":\"ja\",\"reviewBody\":\"今日はCrypto RefillsでVijay Salesのオフラインギフトカードを購入しました。\\n\\n購入と支払いのプロセスはとても簡単でした。\\n\\n次回も間違いなくCrypto Refillsを選びます。\"},{\"locale\":\"ko\",\"r